Package: SIGNAL
Type: Package
Title: Spatial Variable Gene Analysis and Classification
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Tingting", "Hou",
    email = "tingthou@lsu.edu",
    role = c("aut", "cre"),
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0000-0000-0000"))
Description: A unified statistical framework for detecting and classifying
    spatially variable genes (SVGs) in spatial transcriptomics data. SIGNAL
    uses kernel-based variance component decomposition with MINQUE estimation
    to identify unitype SVGs (utSVGs), cell-type-specific SVGs (ctSVGs), and
    spatial-distribution SVGs (sdSVGs) through a two-stage hypothesis testing
    procedure with Benjamini-Yekutieli FDR control.
